OL,3,C'My son only stopped attacking me when
OL,4,Che heard my husband's car'
OL,6,FA mother who was subjected to an hour-
OL,7,Flong attack at the hands of her
OL,8,Fteenage son says she is "scared of
OL,9,Fhim" and the threat he poses on her
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,FThe mum, who has spoken anonymously,
OL,13,Fadopted two boys at a young age, but
OL,14,Fthe elder of the two started showing
OL,15,Fviolent tendencies from the age of
OL,16,Ffive. He has no additional needs, now
OL,17,Fat the age of 13 the threat is getting
OL,18,Fworse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
