OL,3,C'My son only stopped attacking me when
OL,4,Che heard my husband's car'
OL,6,F"I ended up curled up in a ball in the
OL,7,Fcorner of my utility room and he
OL,8,Fpunched and kicked me for about an
OL,9,Fhour," she said. "He only stopped when
OL,10,Fhe heard my husband's car pull into
OL,11,Fthe driveway."
OL,13,FShe says that she is scared to be
OL,14,Falone with the 13-year-old who can
OL,15,F"flip out" at the tiniest thing and,
OL,16,Fduring one outburst, threatened to
OL,17,Fkill her.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
