OL,3,C'My son only stopped attacking me when
OL,4,Che heard my husband's car'
OL,6,F"He picked up a wooden chair and was
OL,7,Ftrying to smash the window", she said.
OL,8,F"He then broke a picture frame and
OL,9,Fthreatened to cut himself. But he said
OL,10,Fwhat he really wanted to do was kill
OL,11,Fme with it."
OL,13,FAnd she is not alone. Hundreds of
OL,14,Fparents across the North West of
OL,15,FEngland are suffering domestic
OL,16,Fviolence at the hands of their
OL,17,Fchildren, with one charity seeing a
OL,18,F70% increase in referrals over the
OL,19,Flast few years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
