OL,6,FParental Education Growth Support
OL,7,F(PEGS), which was set up by a parent
OL,8,Fwho suffered violence from their
OL,9,Fchild, says the problem has previously
OL,10,Fbeen dismissed as "naughty children"
OL,11,Fand parents are often being blamed.
OL,13,FAnother mum, who has also spoken to
OL,14,FGranada Reports anonymously, say she
OL,15,Fhas been bitten by her 11-year-old
OL,16,Fdaughter who is neurodiverse and has
OL,17,Fadditional needs. This is part of her
OL,18,Fviolent and uncontrollable rage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
