OL,6,FThe girl was adopted in Merseyside as
OL,7,Fa baby, but started showing violent
OL,8,Ftendencies from a young age. Her mum
OL,9,Fsays her "uncontrollable rage" has
OL,10,Fgotten worse as she get older and
OL,11,Fstronger.
OL,13,FThe mother explains that she had to
OL,14,Fvideo her daughters violence to prove
OL,15,Fhow bad it was.
