OL,4,Che heard my husband's car'
OL,6,FSpeaking about the footage, she said:
OL,7,F"You can hear at that point that she
OL,8,Fhas gone past any reasonable thought,
OL,9,Fyou can hear the pain in her voice. I
OL,10,Fdon't think unless you see it and hear
OL,11,Fit that you believe it is happening.
OL,13,F"My sister has come into the house as
OL,14,FI have been held up against the wall,
OL,15,Fshe has ripped my clothing. She's
OL,16,Fpunched me in the face. She kicks with
OL,17,Fher shoes on, so I've had bruises all
OL,18,Fover my legs."
