OL,4,Che heard my husband's car'
OL,6,F"She has punched me in the face":
OL,7,FMother describes horrifying abuse she
OL,8,Fhas suffered at the hands of her
OL,9,Fdaughter.
OL,11,FDespite the pain and suffering caused
OL,12,Fby the mental and physical abuse both
OL,13,FMums say they never stop loving their
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,FThe mum from Cheshire said: "It breaks
OL,17,Fyour heart. I love him so so much but
OL,18,FI am scared of him. I am scared to be
OL,19,Fon my own with my son and to say those
OL,20,Fwords out loud is just awful."
