OL,6,FBoth women have been sent on parenting
OL,7,Fcourses and say they feel blamed for
OL,8,Ftheir children's behaviour and say
OL,9,Fthat few people believe or understand
OL,10,Ftheir suffering.
OL,12,FThe mum from Merseyside added: "That
OL,13,Flevel of anger from a child, you don't
OL,14,Fwant to admit to other people because
OL,15,Fyou feel like you've failed it's
OL,16,Fembarrassing."
OL,18,FOne mum says her teenage son
OL,19,Fthreatened to kill her with a broken
OL,20,Fpicture frame.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
