OL,4,Che heard my husband's car'
OL,6,F"It could be that they are struggling
OL,7,Fat school and being bullied outside of
OL,8,Fthe home and that's the only place it
OL,9,Fcan come out because to them it is a
OL,10,Fsafe space to vent. The work we do is
OL,11,Fto try and find the cause."
OL,13,FFor the families suffering the ongoing
OL,14,Fabuse from their children, they want
OL,15,Fto raise awareness of the problem
OL,16,Fwhile protecting themselves and
OL,17,Fhelping their children.
